  "texts": [
    "As an illustration of the example in figure 8(b), near the origin of ρ = 0, inside the white half-disk, there is a RP 3 cycle.",
    "This RP 3 cycle is formed as follows.",
    "The union of this cycle and its image, in the 1: 2 covering map, forms a full S 3 in the covering space.",
    "Hence the smooth Z 2 quotient of the full S 3 near the origin of ρ = 0, is always a RP 3 after the smooth quotient.",
    "Hence there is always a RP 3 cycle at the origin (ρ = 0)."
  ],
